@jbogard I guess you could eliminate null checking for CustomExpressions, and then it's on the user to do their own null checking.
Or Possibly Better Yey.  Have the CustomExpresssions destination type be the source expression type vs the destination expected type.

Either way should work for both this and #1483.  It's just do you want to forgo adding null checks on custom expressions or not?

@ccbristo As @jbogard has said these things should of been caught in the beta, but no one tested it, so it shows up in initial release.
